title: I am having troubles with onnx export
body:
I changed : 
ONNX_EXPORT = True 
in models.py

But i had the following error:

```
Using device: "cuda:0"
1/1 Traceback (most recent call last):
  File "detect.py", line 181, in <module>
    save_images=opt.plot_flag,
  File "detect.py", line 72, in detect
    pred = torch.onnx._export(model, img, 'weights/model.onnx', verbose=True);
```

Somebody has solve this problem?

Thanks
